{"article_id":"XAMrcFPUr9L8RyvC","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON/NEW YORK","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"( ) -","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"President Donald Trump attacked James Comey as a \" weak and untruthful slime ball \" on Friday","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"after the fired former FBI director castigated him as an unethical liar","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"and likened him to a mob moss in a searing new memoir .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"The president fired Comey last May","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"while his agency was investigating potential collusion between Trump ' s campaign and Russia in the 2016 U.S. election in a move","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that led the Justice Department to appoint Special Counsel Robert Mueller","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"to take over a probe","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"that has hung over his presidency .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"\" This president is unethical , and untethered to truth and institutional values , \"","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"Comey said in the book due out Tuesday ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"a copy of which was obtained by .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Trump has often publicly criticized Comey","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"since firing him ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"but escalated his attacks in response to the book .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"\" It was my great honor to fire James Comey ! \"","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Trump said in one of a series of scorching Twitter messages ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"adding","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"that Comey","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"- now one of the Republican president ' s fiercest critics -","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"had been a terrible FBI director .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"The tirade followed news accounts of Comey ' s book , \" A Higher Loyalty : Truth , Lies and Leadership , \"","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"which paints a deeply unflattering picture of Trump ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"comparing him to a mob boss","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"who stresses personal loyalty over the law","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"and has little regard for morality or truth .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"Mueller is looking into","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"whether Trump has sought to obstruct the Russia probe ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"and Comey could be a key witness on that front .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Comey last year accused Trump of pressuring him to pledge loyalty and end a probe","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"involving former national security adviser Michael Flynn ' s contacts with Moscow .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"\" James Comey is a proven LEAKER & LIAR , \"","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"Trump wrote .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"Trump accused Comey of lying to Congress ,","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"but did not specify","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"was he was referring to ,","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"and said","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"the former FBI chief should be prosecuted for leaking classified information .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"Trump has denied any collusion","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"and has called Mueller ' s investigation a witch hunt .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"Comey is conducting a series of media interviews before the book ' s official release .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"Copies of the book were obtained by news outlets on Thursday .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"The interviews are Comey ' s first public comments","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"since he testified before the Senate Intelligence Committee last June ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"when he accused Trump of firing him","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"to undermine the FBI ' s Russia investigation .","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"Just days after Trump fired Comey ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"the president said","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"he did it","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"because of \" this Russia thing . \"","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"Trump has launched a series of attacks since last year against U.S. law enforcement leaders and institutions","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"as the Russia probe pressed forward , in addition to Comey and Mueller .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"\" People will rot in hell","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"for besmirching the reputation the integrity and the professional history of these two men , \"","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"Democratic U.S. Representative Jim Himes said on CNN ,","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"referring to Comey and Mueller , himself a former FBI director .","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"In an offshoot of the Mueller probe , Trump ' s longtime personal lawyer ' s office and home were raided by the Federal Bureau on Investigation on Monday .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"In an interview","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"broadcast on Friday on ABC ' s \" Good Morning America , \" Comey discussed his initial encounters last year with Trump ,","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"who took office on Jan. 20 , 2017 .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"He described Trump as volatile , defensive and concerned more about his own image than about whether Russia meddled in the presidential election .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"A combination of file photos show U.S. President Donald Trump in the White House in Washington , DC , U.S.","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"April 9 , 2018","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"and former FBI Director James Comey on Capitol Hill in Washington , U.S. , June 8 , 2017 .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"/Carlos Barria , Jonathan Ernst/File Photos","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"American intelligence agencies last year said","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"Russia interfered in the election through a campaign of propaganda and hacking in a scheme","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"to sow discord in the United States","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"and help get Trump elected .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Moscow has denied meddling .","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"Comey said","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"he cautioned Trump against ordering an investigation into a salacious intelligence dossier","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"alleging an 2013 encounter","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"involving prostitutes in Moscow .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"The dossier was compiled by former British intelligence officer Christopher Steele about Trump ' s ties to Russia","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"and included an allegation","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"that involved prostitutes","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"urinating on one another in a hotel room","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"while Trump watched .","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"Trump denied the allegations","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"and said","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"he might want the FBI to investigate allegations in the dossier","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"to prove","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"they were untrue ,","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"Comey told ABC .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"\" I said to him ,","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"' Sir that ' s up to you","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"but you want to be careful about that","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"because it might create a narrative","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"that we ' re investigating you personally","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"and , second , it ' s very difficult to prove something didn ' t happen , ' \"","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"Comey said .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"Asked to describe that Jan. 6 , 2017 meeting","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"two weeks before Trump took office ,","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"Comey said :","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"\" Really weird .","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"It was almost an out-of-body experience for me . \"","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"\" I honestly never thought","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"these words would come out of my mouth ,","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"but I don ' t know","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"whether the current president of the United States was with prostitutes","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"peeing on each other in Moscow in 2013 , \"","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"Comey told ABC .","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"\" It ' s possible ,","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"but I don ' t know . \"","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"Comey said","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"the dossier ' s allegations had not been verified by the time","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"he left the FBI .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"Before Trump and Comey met alone ,","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"U.S. intelligence chiefs briefed Trump and his advisers about the Russian election meddling .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"What struck him most ,","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"Comey told ABC ,","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"was that the conversation moved straight into a public relations mode ,","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"what they could say","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"and how they could position Trump .","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"A copy of former FBI director James Comey 's book `` A Higher Loyalty '' is seen in New York City , New York , U.S.","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"April 13 , 2018 .","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"/Soren Larson","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"\" No one , to my recollection , asked ,","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"' So what ' s coming next from the Russians ,","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"how might we stop it ,","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"what ' s the future look like ? ' \"","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"Comey said .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":247,"left":0,"right":246,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":246,"left":1,"right":245,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":245,"left":162,"right":244,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":134,"right":161,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":131,"right":133,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":126,"right":130,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":2,"right":125,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"N